Package eoss.commands

Class Summary
CopyCommand The CopyCommand executes a copy-to-clipboard operation on the TabManager.
CutCommand The CutCommand executes a copy-to-clipboard operation followed immediately by a delete operation to obtain the effect of a cut-to-clipboard operation.
ExitCommand Prompts for save on close.
FormatSelectionCommand  
IndentToMatchCommand The Insert command inserts texts into a given TabManager.
InsertBulletedListCommand This command prompts the user for how many items an HTML Bulleted list should contain and then inserts the HTML for a list of that size.
InsertCommand The Insert command inserts texts into a given TabManager.
InsertDictionaryListCommand Command to insert DictionaryList html code.
InsertNumberedListCommand This command asks how many entries long the list should be and then inserts the html for a NumberedList of that many items into the TabManager given at construction time.
InsertTableCommand This command asks a user what dimensions of table html construct they would like and then inserts it into the TabManager given during construction.
OpenCommand This command opens a JFileChooser dialog and executes the calls to load the file.
